I had the same problem and I solved it. the problem is with IE 7 cookie and I set in my web.cofig 
&lt;authentication mode=&quot;Forms&quot;&gt;
      &lt;forms loginUrl=&quot;Login.aspx&quot; name=&quot;.ASPXAUNTH&quot; defaultUrl=&quot;~/Default.aspx&quot; [b]cookieless=&quot;AutoDetect&quot;[/b] &gt;
      &lt;/forms&gt;
&lt;/authentication&gt;
And now all works fine

